1. *Medved* je veliki i opasan sisar. (The *bear* is a large and dangerous mammal.)
2. Videla sam *medveda* dok sam bila u planinama. (I saw a *bear* when I was in the mountains.)
3. Nekada su ljudi lovili *medvede* radi krzna. (In the past, people hunted *bears* for their fur.)
4. Ukoliko sretnete *medveda* u prirodi, najbolje je da se polako udaljite. (If you encounter a *bear* in nature, it's best to slowly move away.)
5. Ovde ima puno šume i *medvedi* su česti gosti. (There's a lot of forest here and *bears* are common visitors.)
6. *Medvedići* su preslatki kada su mali. (Bear cubs are so cute when they're little.)
7. Ne zaboravi da nosiš *medvedića* sa sobom kad ideš da spavaš. (Don't forget to bring your *teddy bear* with you when you go to sleep.)
8. Većina *medveda* zimi spava u jazbinama. (Most *bears* hibernate in dens during winter.)
9. Na izletu smo videli tragove *medveda* u pesku. (On the trip, we saw *bear* tracks in the sand.)
10. Lovci su uspeli da uhvate velikog *medveda* koji je harao selom. (Hunters managed to catch a large *bear* that was wreaking havoc in the village.)